Damaturu- Senator Ibrahim Mohammed Bomai, on Tuesday donated the sum of N2 million to victims of the recent fire outbreak at Potiskum Central Market of Yobe State. Property worth millions of naira were destroyed by the inferno of early hours of yesterday Monday, as a result of unknown surge from one of the shops around 2:30 a.m. Senator Ibrahim Mohammed Bomai, who represents Yobe south Senatorial District, comprising of Potiskum, Nangere, Fune and Fika local government areas of the state presented the donation through his representatives led by Alhaji Buhari Bodori in Potiskum Town when they visited the area to commiserate with the shop owners. EXPOSED - HOW LAGOS DOCTOR DISCOVERED MAJOR REASONS WHY MOST WIVES NOW HEAVILY CHEATS ON THEIR HUSBANDS AND THE PERMANENT SECRET TO SEXUALLY SATISFYING THEIR WIVES. DON'T BE A VICTIM! Speaking with Daily Independent on Telephone, the senator revealed that he was touched with the disaster and urged the victims to take it easy. According to him, the donation is just a token to bring little relief to the affected, so that the pain would be bearable. NIMC Adopts Booking System For NIN Enrolment FCTA Task Team Warns Shop Owners To Comply With COVID-19 Guidelines Or Have Their Businesses Shut Down He commiserated with the affected traders and prayed that God would prevent future occurrence and replenish what they lost in the inferno. Responding, One of the affected shop owners, Malam Usman, thanked the senator for the gesture and prayed for God’s continued provision for him. Usman, who said that property worth large amount of money was destroyed in his shop, called on government and other well-to-do Nigerians to come to the rescue of the shop owners. Also speaking, the Chairman of the United Marketers Association (UMAPO) Potiskum chapter, Nasiru Alhaji Mato thanked all the donors for their contributions to the victims “this will go a long way in alleviating the sufferings of my members, we are indeed grateful to all for the concern to our plights.” SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION